			<item>
				<title>Espiral</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/projects/espiral/</link>
				<pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 09:00:00 -0700</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/espiral/</guid>
				<description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Espiral means &amp;ldquo;spiral&amp;rdquo; in Portuguese.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex justify-center w-full my-16 px-4 md:px-0&#34; style=&#34;margin-bottom: 32px; margin-top: 32px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;figure class=&#34;flex flex-col items-center max-w-full&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/espiral.png&#34; data-lightbox =&#34;gallery &#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img &#xA;        src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/espiral.png&#34; &#xA;        alt=&#34;Espiral cover image&#34; &#xA;        loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300&#34;&#xA;      /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Espiral is a game I made in Twine for the &lt;a href=&#34;https://itch.io/jam/last-3-minutes-jam&#34;&gt;Last 3 Minutes Jam&lt;/a&gt; about a anxious person having to face their interview in the next three minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It has 3 endings, but just 2 are actually very different. The main theme is anxiety and low self-esteem, and how that triggers overthinking to the point of panic and giving up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Customer Cat</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/projects/customer-cat/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 09:00:00 -0700</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/customer-cat/</guid>
				<description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex justify-center w-full my-16 px-4 md:px-0&#34; style=&#34;margin-bottom: 32px; margin-top: 32px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;figure class=&#34;flex flex-col items-center max-w-full&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat.png&#34; data-lightbox =&#34;gallery &#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img &#xA;        src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat.png&#34; &#xA;        alt=&#34;Customer Cat cover image&#34; &#xA;        loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;        class=&#34;w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300&#34;&#xA;      /&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A game about an entitled cat that lives in a gated community and decided to buy a soda and bully a minimum-wage worker.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; width: 100%; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15x; padding: 0 16px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;flex justify-center w-full my-16 px-4 md:px-0&#34; style=&#34;margin-bottom: 32px; margin-top: 32px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figure class=&#34;flex flex-col items-center max-w-full&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat/screenshot_1.png&#34; data-lightbox =&#34;gallery &#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img &#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat/screenshot_1.png&#34; &#xA;            alt=&#34;Customer Cat cover image&#34; &#xA;            loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;            class=&#34;w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300&#34;&#xA;          /&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;        &#xA;      &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;flex justify-center w-full my-16 px-4 md:px-0&#34; style=&#34;margin-bottom: 32px; margin-top: 32px;&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;figure class=&#34;flex flex-col items-center max-w-full&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &#xA;        &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat/screenshot_2.png&#34; data-lightbox =&#34;gallery &#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img &#xA;            src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/customer_cat/screenshot_2.png&#34; &#xA;            alt=&#34;Customer Cat cover image&#34; &#xA;            loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;            class=&#34;w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-md md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl h-auto object-contain rounded-lg shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300&#34;&#xA;          /&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;        &#xA;      &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The game is really short and a walk and talk simulation, but it was fun to make as a way to learn Defold. Your objective is to get the cat to buy a soda can and bully a worker.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
